    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来投影是一款结合了老派第一人称射击游戏玩法与现代图形的第一人称射击游戏， 为你带来简洁而清新的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三种独特的武器</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷你枪可以收集敌人的子弹并将其反弹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量武器可以与环境进行互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重力枪将来袭的子弹反弹回敌人的头部。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211620/extras/73187fa0a6b21a36c98aaae361409475.poster.avif?t=1727549449\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211620/extras/73187fa0a6b21a36c98aaae361409475.webm?t=1727549449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用能量武器改变环境和利用跑酷功能来击败敌人。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过跑墙越过障碍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持你已经通过冲刺和滑行改变的环境。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211620/extras/c3c85e76febd79545d630e36c7563541.poster.avif?t=1727549449\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211620/extras/c3c85e76febd79545d630e36c7563541.webm?t=1727549449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从街头帮派到最高执法机构，所有人都在对抗你。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的街头帮派只会骚扰你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精英士兵可以用他们先进的武器和训练来试图阻止你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲和赛博忍者是你最强大的敌人。</p></li></ul>",
